         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#CMR">
            <p>[The Council] and the People [honou]red Kallipp[os, son of Me]trodoros, [son of Ka]llippos Kor[-], with the fin[est and] greate[st honou]rs; 
               a man of a fi[rst] fam[ily ?having lived for virtue . . .</p>
